	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It is certainly an interesting thing as a DIY project, and would be especially cool as an open source HW/SW project, but I should note that these days there is a ton of cheap Chinese portable consoles (Dingoo, Gemei, Caanoo, Ritmix, and countless others) with emulators, some of them also has TV out. I also recall something similar that had no screen, just a small box with USB and TV out. So if someone just wants a ready-made product, there are existing devices already.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
